{
  "texts": [
    "Videos depicting PCI and CABG procedures were also removed.",
    "Any videos that did not display recognizable coronary artery segments as determined by Algorithm 5 were excluded.",
    "To facilitate video-level predictions, we maintained a single video for each artery segment in a DICOM after the application of Algorithm 5.",
    "All datasets comprise examinations from patients exhibiting a range of conditions: multiple stenoses, a single stenosis, or no stenosis at all.",
    "Detailed video counts for each scenario are provided in Supplementary Tables 1 and 2."
  ]
}